    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom-ready condition, reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship and uncompromising maintenance. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, adheres to the highest standards of excellence. For the discerning driver who demands nothing short of perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly superlative machine. We invite rigorous inspection to confirm its pristine status.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
