      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited to show you this car\u2014it\u2019s an absolute dream! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is basically untouched. It drives as smooth as silk and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. You really have to see it to believe how pristine it is! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
